                        No. 2020 /
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="section_cus">
                    <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" class="tableCustom">
                        <tbody>
                            <tr>
                                <td class="text_left col_2">
                                    <p>
                                        Serial No. ................................ <br>
                                        Date of Receipt ........................ <br>
                                        Receiving Official (initial..................)
