                                    <p>Dated.....................201</p>
                                </td>
                            </tr>

                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                </div>

                <div class="latter_sec_full">
                    <p>Gentlemen, <br>
                        I..........................................................................................beg
                        to state that I am
                        (in block letters)
                        already a member of the Society of which I hold at present...............................
                        Shares of Rs. 10/- each. My membership number is...........................................
                        I now request you to kindly allot me................additional shares of Rs. 10/- each</p>
                </div>


                <div class="section_cus">
                    <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" class="tableCustom">
                        <tbody>


                            <tr>
                                <td class="text_left col_2 border_td">
                                    <p>
                                        From...................to................. <br>
                                        Distinctive number alloted. <br>
                                        ........................................ <br>
                                        <b>Signature of officia</b>
                                    </p>
                                </td>
                                <td class="text_left align_top col_2">
                                    <p>Yours faithfully <br> <br>
                                        .................................................
                                        <b>(Full Signature)</b> <br>
                                        Designation............................. <br>
                                        Dept./Office.............................
                                    </p>
