                    <p class="small_text">N. B. -

                        (1) Value of shares must be paid within 30 days of allotment (excluding the
                        date of sanction). <br>
                        (2) Last date of submission of shares application is 10th of each month.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <button class="btn btn-primary" type="button" onclick="printDiv();">Print</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>